beer.beer_description:
We’ve proudly partnered with Fourpure Brewing Co in Bermondsey to bring you this juicy and tropical session IPA. Combining modern hop types with a crisp malt body creates a full flavoured IPA at 4% abv with fruity notes and a pleasant hop finish that’s uniquely its own. Four cans per pack. Suitable for vegans.
Juicy & Tropical, Suitable for vegans
